  "body": "Please see the comment from @ibrkhalil  before fixing this one https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15190#issuecomment-1454684319\r\n\r\n> Apparently, When the user edits an image with a photo .. The photo gets lost .. So the team have added a constaint to prevent editing a photo with text on status-go [here](https://github.com/status-im/status-go/blob/999d8c0ee0f2274c58b5a2de3beddab7feaabd16/protocol/messenger_messages.go#L19) .. Happy to investigate in a subsequent issue\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Go to any chat\r\n2. Send a message that contains some text and an image\r\n3. Long press the message -> Tap 'edit'\r\n4. Update text\r\n\r\n#### Actual result:\r\nThe text is not updated\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/222458375-d7d1ce76-6605-4688-9ccf-5de81c4d2d99.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected result:\r\nText is updated\r\n\r\n#### Env: \r\nnightly 2 Mar 2023",
